Description: Simple GUI for Bup, a very efficient backup system
 Bups is a graphical user interface for Bup, allowing you to manage
 backup configurations, run backups, and browse backup contents through
 a modern GTK4 interface.
 .
 Features include backup scheduling via anacron or systemd, encrypted
 filesystem support via encfs, SSHFS and CIFS mounts, and a clean
 libadwaita-based GNOME interface.
